data.description: Finding homebuying a challenge right now? This seller is willing to pay up to but not exceeding $10,000 in closing costs, prepaids, and fees with an acceptable offer! New in 2022: roof, water heater, and flooring. Great 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with an eat-in kitchen featuring a double pantry, plenty of cabinets and countertop, breakfast bar, and a breakfast nook with bay windows. Needing a fridge? The fridge stays! Big primary suite with a spacious bath showcasing a big walk-in closet, separate jet tub and shower, and dual vanity. Nice backyard with patio and wood privacy fence. Call today about this great opportunity to own a home of your own!
